paaf.assignment_type = 'E' AND paaf.legislation_code = 'CA' AND ppos.date_start = ( SELECT MAX(ppos1.date_start) FROM per_periods_of_service ppos1, per_all_assignments_m paam1 WHERE paam1.person_id = paaf.person_id AND paam1.period_of_service_id = ppos1.period_of_service_id AND paam1.assignment_type = 'E' AND paam1.primary_assignment_flag = 'Y' AND paam1.primary_work_relation_flag = 'Y' AND paam1.legislation_code = 'CA' AND paam1.permanent_temporary_flag ='R' AND trunc(ppos1.date_start) <= trunc(pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE')) AND trunc(pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE')) BETWEEN paam1.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE AND paam1.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND paam1.legal_entity_id NOT IN ( SELECT ORGANIZATION_ID FROM HR_LEGAL_ENTITIES WHERE 1 = 1 AND STATUS = 'A' AND CLASSIFICATION_CODE = 'HCM_LEMP' AND trunc(pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE')) BETWEEN EFFECTIVE_START_DATE AND EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND NAME IN ('WESCO Blended Leader Holding Entity') --AND NAME IN (SELECT MEANING FROM HCM_LOOKUPS WHERE ENABLED_FLAG = 'Y' AND LOOKUP_TYPE = 'WCC_HR_WESCO_LEGAL_EMP_LKP') --Future Query ) ) AND ((ppos.actual_termination_date IS NULL) OR ( trunc(ppos.actual_termination_date) > (pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE') - pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('Include_Term_Days')) AND paaf.action_code <> 'GLB_TRANSFER' ) OR ( ppos.last_updated_by <> 'FUSION_APPS_HCM_ESS_LOADER_APPID' AND trunc(ppos.last_update_date) > (pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE') - pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('Include_Term_Days')) AND paaf.action_code <> 'GLB_TRANSFER' ) )
AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM hcm_lookups WHERE lookup_code = papf.person_number AND lookup_type = 'AXE_HR_MS_EXCEPTION_LOOKUP' AND enabled_flag = 'Y' )
